 and an asymmetrical caudal fin.<ref name="foster-morrolepis" /> Adult specimens would reach about 20&nbsp;cm in length and 113 g (4&nbsp;oz) in mass.<ref name="foster-morrolepis" /> |- | ''[[Potamoceratodus]]'' | ''P. guentheri'' | * Colorado | | | Once thought to be a species of ''[[Ceratodus]]''. |- |}
