ical engineering |year=2002 |last1=Devedzić |first1=Vladan |journal=Communications of the ACM |volume=45 |issue=4 |pages=136|citeseerx=10.1.1.218.7546 }} * Sure, York, Staab, Steffen and Studer, Rudi (2009). Ontology Engineering Methodology. In Staab, Steffen & [[Rudi_Studer|Studer, Rudi]] (eds.) Handbook on Ontologies (2nd edition), Springer-Verlag, Heidelberg. {{ISBN|978-3-540-70999-2}}
